TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Objective: Finish building your base, then find and destory the enemy base in the south east. You may be attacked!

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Press 'l' (that's an L) to see where you have radar coverage.
Hold down shift when giving orders to your commander to queue up multiple orders.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: To move units in lines, select the unit, then hold the right mouse button and draw a line.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Don't forget that you can use your com to guard your lab and help it build.
